        <abstract>
            <p>The flint tools found at Bedford.</p>
            <p>Further discussion of Jamieson’s theory of the formation of the roads of Glen Roy by a glacial lake. Comments on formation of Glen Spean terraces. Mentions glaciers in North Wales.</p> 
<p>Agreement with John Murray to publish [<hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>].</p> 
        </abstract>
